We recommended the following courses of action:
1. The LGU HRMO together with the key official prioritize the hiring of the additional technical personnel in the MEO;
2. The Municipal Engineering Office in its annual planning consider the allocation of work to its personnel to local and trust funds in order to avoid confusion of work assignments, thus, inefficiency of the workers;
3. The Municipal Engineering Office must coordinate with the Municipal Planning Office to come up with the achievable priority PPA to avoid the problem in the identification of sites; and
4. The LGU will study the creation of a monitoring team to take charge of monitoring the implementation of all the infrastructure projects.

